data.description: Here's your chance to own this beautiful, very clean home priced below market value located at Spanos  Park West built in 2009 with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2143 sq. of living space, formal living and dining areas, separate family room with fireplace, tile and laminate floors, granite  countertops, stainless steel appliances, plantation shutters ,huge master with separate shower and soaking tub, walk in closet, double vanities in baths;upstairs  laundry with sink and cabinets, ceiling fans in all rooms; Short walk to Manilo Silva Elem. School, Lodi school district, close to shopping, restaurants, freeway and more. Come check this gorgeous home in  a desirable, quiet neighborhood!
